fullText: ⚠️ Heads-up to anyone using the DeepSeek-V3.2-Exp inference demo: earlier versions had a RoPE implementation mismatch in the indexer module that could degrade performance. Indexer RoPE expects non-interleaved input, MLA RoPE expects interleaved. Fixed in https://t.co/2BDzSyt1cW.
